  body
    section.preloader
      .spinner
        span.sk-inner-circle

    main
      nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg
        .container
          button.navbar-toggler(type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation")
            span.navbar-toggler-icon

          a.navbar-brand(href="/homepage")
            strong
              span Family
              |  Guy

          .d-lg-none
            if user && user.username
              a.custom-icon.me-3(href="/profile") 
                span.ms-1.fs-6= user.username
                i.bi-person
            else
              a.bi-person.custom-icon.me-3(href="/login")
            a.bi-bag.custom-icon(href="/product-detail")

          #navbarNav.collapse.navbar-collapse
            ul.navbar-nav.mx-auto
              li.nav-item
                a.nav-link.active(href="/homepage") Home
              li.nav-item
                a.nav-link(href="/about") About
              li.nav-item
                a.nav-link(href="/products") Products
              li.nav-item
                a.nav-link(href="/faq") FAQs
              li.nav-item
                a.nav-link(href="/contact") Contact

            .d-none.d-lg-block
              if user && user.username
                a.custom-icon.me-3(href="/profile") 
                  span.ms-1.fs-5= user.username
                  i.bi-person
              else
                a.bi-person.custom-icon.me-3(href="/login")
              a.bi-bag.custom-icon(href="/product-detail")

      section.slick-slideshow
        .slick-custom
          img.img-fluid(src="images/slideshow/medium-shot-business-women-high-five.jpeg" alt="")
          .slick-bottom
            .container
              .row
                .col-lg-6.col-10
                  h1.slick-title Cool Fashion
                  p.lead.text-white.mt-lg-3.mb-lg-5
                    | Little fashion template comes with total 8 HTML pages provided by Tooplate website.
                  a.btn.custom-btn(href="/about") Learn more about us

        .slick-custom
          img.img-fluid(src="images/slideshow/team-meeting-renewable-energy-project.jpeg" alt="")
          .slick-bottom
            .container
              .row
                .col-lg-6.col-10
                  h1.slick-title New Design
                  p.lead.text-white.mt-lg-3.mb-lg-5
                    | Please share this Little Fashion template to your friends. Thank you for supporting us.
                  a.btn.custom-btn(href="/products") Explore products

        .slick-custom
          img.img-fluid(src="images/slideshow/two-business-partners-working-together-office-computer.jpeg" alt="")
          .slick-bottom
            .container
              .row
                .col-lg-6.col-10
                  h1.slick-title Talk to us
                  p.lead.text-white.mt-lg-3.mb-lg-5
                    | Tooplate is one of the best HTML CSS template websites for everyone.
                  a.btn.custom-btn(href="/contact") Work with us

      section.about.section-padding
        .container
          .row
            .col-12.text-center
              h2.mb-5
                | Get started with 
                span Little
                |  Fashion

            .col-lg-2.col-12.mt-auto.mb-auto
              ul#pills-tab.nav.nav-pills.mb-5.mx-auto.justify-content-center.align-items-center(role="tablist")
                li.nav-item(role="presentation")
                  button#pills-home-tab.nav-link.active(data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#pills-home" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-home" aria-selected="true")
                    | Introduction
                li.nav-item(role="presentation")
                  button#pills-youtube-tab.nav-link(data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#pills-youtube" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-youtube" aria-selected="true")
                    | How we work?
                li.nav-item(role="presentation")
                  button#pills-skill-tab.nav-link(data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#pills-skill" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-skill" aria-selected="false")
                    | Capabilites

            .col-lg-10.col-12
              #pills-tabContent.tab-content.mt-2
                #pills-home.tab-pane.fade.show.active(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-home-tab")
                  .row
                    .col-lg-7.col-12
                      img.img-fluid(src="images/pim-chu-z6NZ76_UTDI-unsplash.jpeg" alt="")
                    .col-lg-5.col-12
                      .d-flex.flex-column.h-100.ms-lg-4.mt-lg-0.mt-5
                        h4.mb-3
                          | Good 
                          span Design
                          br
                          | Ideas for 
                          span your
                          |  fashion
                        p
                          | Little Fashion templates comes with 
                          a(href="/login") sign in
                          |  / 
                          a(href="/register") sign up
                          |  pages, product listing / product detail, about, FAQs, and contact page.
                        p
                          | Since this HTML template is based on Boostrap 5 CSS library, you can feel free to add more components as you need.
                        .mt-2.mt-lg-auto
                          a.custom-link.mb-2(href="/about")
                            | Learn more about us
                            i.bi-arrow-right.ms-2

                #pills-youtube.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-youtube-tab")
                  .row
                    .col-lg-7.col-12
                      .ratio.ratio-16x9
                        iframe(src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/f_7JqPDWhfw?controls=0" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen)
                    .col-lg-5.col-12
                      .d-flex.flex-column.h-100.ms-lg-4.mt-lg-0.mt-5
                        h4.mb-3 Life at Studio
                        p
                          | Over three years in business, We've had the chance to work on a variety of projects, with companies
                        p Custom work is branding, web design, UI/UX design
                        .mt-2.mt-lg-auto
                          a.custom-link.mb-2(href="/contact")
                            | Work with us
                            i.bi-arrow-right.ms-2

                #pills-skill.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-skill-tab")
                  .row
                    .col-lg-7.col-12
                      img.img-fluid(src="images/cody-lannom-G95AReIh_Ko-unsplash.jpeg" alt="")
                    .col-lg-5.col-12
                      .d-flex.flex-column.h-100.ms-lg-4.mt-lg-0.mt-5
                        h4.mb-3 What can help you?
                        p
                          | Over three years in business, We've had the chance on projects
                        .skill-thumb.mt-3
                          strong Branding
                          span.float-end 90%
                          .progress
                            .progress-bar.progress-bar-primary(role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="90" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 90%")
                          
                          strong Design & Stragety
                          span.float-end 70%
                          .progress
                            .progress-bar.progress-bar-primary(role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="70" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 70%")
                          
                          strong Online Platform
                          span.float-end 80%
                          .progress
                            .progress-bar.progress-bar-primary(role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="80" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 80%")
                        
                        .mt-2.mt-lg-auto
                          a.custom-link.mb-2(href="/products")
                            | Explore products
                            i.bi-arrow-right.ms-2

      section.front-product
        .container-fluid.p-0
          .row.align-items-center
            .col-lg-6.col-12
              img.img-fluid(src="images/retail-shop-owner-mask-social-distancing-shopping.jpg" alt="")
            .col-lg-6.col-12
              .px-5.py-5.py-lg-0
                h2.mb-4
                  span Retail
                  |  shop owners
                p.lead.mb-4
                  | Credits go to Unsplash and FreePik websites for images used in this Little Fashion by Tooplate.
                a.custom-link(href="/products")
                  | Explore Products
                  i.bi-arrow-right.ms-2

